OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FBy ITV News Multimedia Producer Connor
OL,7,FParker
OL,9,FThe United States and Iran have
OL,10,Freached an interim deal aimed at
OL,11,Fending the war and reopening the
OL,12,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FThe deal is expected to be signed in
OL,15,FSwitzerland on Friday.
OL,17,FBut while some of the main commitments
OL,18,Fare known, the exact details of the
OL,19,Fagreement have not yet been published
OL,20,F- and numerous thorny issues have been
OL,21,Fleft unresolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
