OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThis means nobody knows if the deal
OL,7,Fwill last.
OL,9,FIt is quickly becoming controversial
OL,10,Fin the US, with some of Trump's
OL,11,FRepublican Party already criticising
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Israel has also said it
OL,15,Fwill not withdraw from land seized in
OL,16,FLebanon and plans to continue its
OL,17,Fcampaign against Hezbollah.
OL,19,FThis is despite Iran tying the interim
OL,20,Fdeal to halting Israel's attacks on
OL,21,FHezbollah in Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
