OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FBoth the US and Israel launched the
OL,7,Fwar on February 28, striking numerous
OL,8,Ftargets in Iran, with Iran responding
OL,9,Fby blocking the Strait and attacking
OL,10,FUS allies in the region. Israel
OL,11,Finvaded Lebanon weeks later.
OL,13,FA ceasefire was agreed on April 8, but
OL,14,Ftensions remained high with the US
OL,15,Fblockading Iran's ports and Iran
OL,16,Frefusing to open the Strait.
OL,18,FNations across the world have been
OL,19,Feager for the conflict to end amid
OL,20,Ffears of the impact on the global
OL,21,Feconomy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
