OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FWorld leaders and international
OL,7,Fmarkets have welcomed the agreement,
OL,8,Fwith all sides keen to see the Strait
OL,9,Fof Hormuz reopened. There is a huge
OL,10,Fincentive to make the deal a permanent
OL,11,Fpeace.
OL,13,FHere is what to know about it.
OL,15,FA 60-day period to attempt to address
OL,16,FIran's nuclear programme
OL,18,FThe US and Israel fear Iran's nuclear
OL,19,Fprogramme could lead to an atomic
OL,20,Fweapon, and it was a main reason their
OL,21,Fleaders cited for going to war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
