OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FTehran has insisted its nuclear
OL,7,Fprogramme is peaceful, though it has
OL,8,Fenough highly enriched uranium to
OL,9,Fbuild several atomic bombs, should it
OL,10,Fchoose to do so.
OL,12,FA senior US administration official
OL,13,Ftold the Associated Press on Friday
OL,14,Fthat the emerging agreement would
OL,15,Fbegin the process of destroying or
OL,16,Fremoving Tehran's highly enriched
OL,17,Furanium.
OL,19,FThat's something disputed by Iran,
OL,20,Fwhich has insisted it would hold onto
OL,21,Fits stockpile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe official said the 60 days would be
OL,7,Fused to work out technical details for
OL,8,Fremoving the uranium.
OL,10,FThe official did not say who the US
OL,11,Fenvisions taking charge of removing
OL,12,Fthe uranium, which is believed to be
OL,13,Fentombed under three nuclear sites
OL,14,Fbattered by US strikes last year.
OL,16,FRussia has also offered to take the
OL,17,Fmaterial.
OL,19,FThe Strait of Hormuz may be reopened
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
