OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe US official the Associated Press
OL,7,Fspoke to said the emerging agreement
OL,8,Fincludes provisions for reopening the
OL,9,Fstrait, a crucial waterway for global
OL,10,Foil and gas transport.
OL,12,FIran Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,13,Fsaid the country wants a deal that
OL,14,Fallows Tehran to charge ships "for
OL,15,Fservices rendered" when they transit
OL,16,Fthe Strait.
OL,18,FIran started charging vessels for
OL,19,Fpassage during the war, which the US
OL,20,Fand other nations have said violates
OL,21,Finternational law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FIran has also said it will only reopen
OL,7,Fthe Strait if the US ends the blockade
OL,8,Fof its ports.
OL,10,FThe Strait has long been considered
OL,11,Finternational waters, though it lies
OL,12,Fwithin the territorial waters of Iran
OL,13,Fand Oman.
OL,15,FTransit through the Strait has
OL,16,Fdisrupted global energy supplies,
OL,17,Fdriven up fuel prices, and made food
OL,18,Fand other basics like fertiliser more
OL,19,Fexpensive well beyond the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
