OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FWhen US President Donald Trump
OL,7,Fannounced the deal on Sunday, he said:
OL,8,F"I hereby fully authorise the toll
OL,9,Ffree opening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Fand, simultaneously herewith,
OL,11,Fauthorise the immediate removal of the
OL,12,FUnited States Naval blockade. Ships of
OL,13,Fthe World, start your engines. Let the
OL,14,Foil flow!"
OL,16,FWhat will happen to Lebanon remains
OL,17,Funclear
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
