CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe prime minister of Pakistan, who
OL,7,Fhas been acting as a mediator, said
OL,8,Fafter the deal had been announced that
OL,9,F"both sides have declared the
OL,10,Fimmediate and permanent termination of
OL,11,Fmilitary operations on all fronts,
OL,12,Fincluding in Lebanon".
OL,14,FBut Israel has seemingly rejected that.
OL,16,FDefence Minister Israel Katz said the
OL,17,Fcountry will not withdraw from land
OL,18,Fseized in Lebanon as the interim deal
OL,19,Fis pending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
