OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKatz said Israel plans to stay
OL,12,F"indefinitely" in lands it holds in
OL,13,FLebanon, as well as Syria and the Gaza
OL,14,FStrip.
OL,16,FKatz also threatened that if Iran
OL,17,Fattacks Israel, Israel will strike
OL,18,FIran with "great force".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
