OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FDespite a ceasefire between Lebanon
OL,7,Fand Israel being in place, Israel and
OL,8,FHezbollah, which is based in Lebanon,
OL,9,Fhave been fighting nearly continuously
OL,10,Ffor months.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, hours before the US and
OL,13,FIran agreed on the deal, Israel
OL,14,Flaunched strikes on Beirut targeting
OL,15,FHezbollah.
OL,17,FTrump criticised this after both the
OL,18,FUS and Iran warned against attacking
OL,19,FBeirut directly while the peace talks
OL,20,Fwere ongoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781547074
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FHezbollah has repeatedly said it does
OL,7,Fnot recognise deals signed by Lebanon
OL,8,Fand has vowed to continue fighting
OL,9,Fwith Israel as long as they maintain a
OL,10,Fpresence in Lebanon.
OL,12,FThe US could pay Iran a lot of money
OL,14,FThree regional officials said the
OL,15,Femerging deal was expected to include
OL,16,Fthe phased lifting of sanctions on
OL,17,FIran and the release of frozen Iranian
OL,18,Fassets, which amount to tens of
OL,19,Fbillions of dollars.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
